  30 Oct 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  -vmware-modules-1.0.0.8.ebuild:
  Removed verion 0.0.8 since we have removed the only VMware product (VMware
  Workstation 3.2.1) that used it.

